Ms. Lu,

3
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,799
Mr. Shen added four extra guests today.

4
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,519
Let them use this private room.

5
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:48,680
Okay.

6
00:01:59,848 --> 00:02:03,934
(Lu Ting, Manager of Shen Mo's Club)

7
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:10,472
(The Unbearable Weight of Love)

8
00:02:11,976 --> 00:02:14,792
=Episode 21=
(Idealistic Love)

9
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:26,280
- Congrats, Mr. Dong.
- Mr. Dong.

10
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,319
- Congrats.
- Mr. Dong.

11
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,199
- Congrats, Mr. Dong.
- Congrats.

12
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:30,680
Remember to treat us all to a meal.

13
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:31,960
Congrats, Mr. Dong.

14
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:32,919
Congrats, Mr. Dong.

15
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:33,560
Ever upward!

16
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,039
Congrats, Mr. Dong.

17
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:35,599
Congrats.

18
00:02:35,599 --> 00:02:36,479
Let's drink tonight.

19
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,199
- Congrats
- Congrats.

20
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:45,000
Mr. Dong, good morning.

21
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,439
Stop teasing me.

22
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:47,960
Let's meet soon.

23
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,088
Congrats, Mr. Dong.

24
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:52,120
Do you mind using Xu's old office?

25
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:54,400
If you do,
I'll have someone renovate it.

26
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:55,479
I don't mind.

27
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:56,560
Alright.

28
00:02:57,520 --> 00:03:00,240
If you have any special requests,
just tell me.

29
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:01,879
Thanks.

30
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,120
Congrats, Mr. Dong.

31
00:03:04,479 --> 00:03:06,319
- Congrats, Mr. Dong.
- Congrats, Mr. Dong.

32
