- Mr. Dong.
- Congrats, Mr. Dong.

33
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:08,360
Congrats.

34
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,120
Treat us to dinner tonight, Mr. Dong.

35
00:03:10,199 --> 00:03:11,199
- Dinner!
- Dinner!

36
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:13,400
Congrats, Mr. Dong.

37
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,680
Congrats, Mr. Dong.

38
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,479
Thank you, everyone.

39
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,319
You're the best.

40
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,319
Let's not get complacent.

41
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:20,319
Let's keep up the hard work, okay?

42
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:20,960
Okay.

43
00:03:21,479 --> 00:03:22,680
You're the best.

44
00:03:29,288 --> 00:03:30,879
(Congrats, Dong Yue!
All the best in the new chapter)

45
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:32,479
(of your career.
GST China management Dpt.)

46
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:33,080
Mr. Dong,

47
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,840
I'm so happy.

48
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:37,400
This is my happiest day this year.

49
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,080
Here.

50
00:03:41,319 --> 00:03:42,599
What? It's out of production.

51
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:45,360
Once this bottle's gone, it's gone.

52
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,039
I can't take it. You keep it.

53
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:51,479
No. This is for you.

54
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,840
Fine wine for a hero.

55
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,919
This wine belongs with you.
That's where it should be.

56
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,680
It'd be wasted at my place.

57
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,840
I'd feel sorry for it.

58
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:00,960
Then thank you.

59
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,000
Mr. Dong,

60
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:05,800
you asked me to look into Lu Ting.
I found something.

61
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:11,280
She seems to be working
at Shen Mo's private club now.

62
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:14,159
She's responsible
for the entire club's event operations.

63
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:19,199
I heard Lu Ting is the one
who bribed Zhao Mei.

64
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:23,959
Could it be that Shen Mo arranged it
behind the scenes?

65
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:27,279
Big shots are big shots for a reason.

66
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:28,800
They don't act lightly.

67
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,360
But when they do, it's a knockout.

68
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:32,639
Who can withstand such tactics?

69
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:35,399
But with you, he really has been...

70
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,720
I don't know anything.

71
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,240
I'll get back to work now.

72
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:03,519
I'm new here.

73
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:05,800
How about I treat you all to lunch?

74
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,560
It's okay. No need.

75
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,680
If you're all busy,

76
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:15,279
I can pick it up.

77
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:16,800
Many new places are nearby.

78
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:17,959
What do you want to eat?

79
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:18,800
Don't be polite.

80
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,120
I'm not being polite.

81
00:05:20,279 --> 00:05:21,439
I'm trying to lose weight.

82
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,600
Never mind.

83
00:05:29,319 --> 00:05:30,680
I'm a complete mess right now.

84
00:05:31,279 --> 00:05:31,879
What's wrong?

85
00:05:32,839 --> 00:05:34,839
I planned to come clean
with the company today.

86
00:05:35,439 --> 00:05:37,560
But Wang Hao took the blame for me.

87
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,800
He said the dog was a gift to him.

88
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:40,600
What?

89
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:42,560
What did the company say?

90
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:45,319
The company thinks
it's overstaffed anyway,

91
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:47,600
so when he offered to leave,

92
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:50,024
they signed
the severance agreement right away.

93
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:51,879
He is so silly.

94
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,120
We're teeing off. Hurry up.

95
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:55,800
Coming.

96
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:58,360
Go ahead, scold me.

97
00:05:58,879 --> 00:06:01,040
I can't be there when you need me most.

98
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,360
I'm playing golf with Shen Mo.

99
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,439
He'll check into the hospital soon.

100
00:06:05,439 --> 00:06:06,879
I'm trying to lift his spirits.

101
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,079
Why would I scold you?

102
00:06:08,079 --> 00:06:09,560
I'm too busy scolding myself.

103
00:06:10,879 --> 00:06:12,879
Both of us
need to look out for ourselves.

104
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,519
Wait for me to come back.

105
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,439
Bye.

106
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:16,279
Please have a seat.

107
00:06:16,279 --> 00:06:16,959
Just a moment.

108
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:17,879
Okay. Thank you.

109
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,000
What are you doing here?

110
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,800
Small world, isn't it?

111
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:35,079
I was at a meeting at a nearby hotel.

112
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,560
You guys have such comfortable jobs.

113
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:44,480
Not like us working around the clock.

114
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:48,800
We can hold meetings anywhere
as long as there's a phone signal.

115
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:52,680
The work never ends.

116
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,120
For you,

117
00:06:57,560 --> 00:07:00,439
having work and a job to go to
is something to be grateful for.

118
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:05,000
Besides, aren't you sneaking out
during work hours to do your hair too?

119
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,360
You seem pretty idle to me.

120
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:11,839
Is Li Dongming in the meeting here too?

121
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,319
He didn't come.

122
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,360
I'm no longer on his team.

123
00:07:24,319 --> 00:07:25,439
He transferred me out.

124
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,720
Hello. Any hairstyle requests today?

125
00:07:32,199 --> 00:07:32,759
The usual.

126
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:33,439
Got it.

127
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,319
Thank you.

128
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,720
What a coincidence today!

129
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,199
We have the same hairstyle.

130
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:58,248
It's nice.

131
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,720
Given that,

132
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:00,920
let's take a photo.

133
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,120
I'll send it to you.

134
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:07,560
Whatever.

135
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:18,199
As you all know very well,

136
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:23,079
our company's CEO rotation election
is about to begin.

137
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:27,040
This is an excellent opportunity
for all of you.

138
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:30,240
Having served the company
for so many years,

139
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:34,840
I understand deeply how crucial
this position is to the company

140
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:37,240
and for our development.

141
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,440
You're all young,

142
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:41,960
energetic,

143
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,399
and experienced.

144
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:46,720
Whether Senior Partners
or general partners,

145
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,759
I believe everyone has a chance.

146
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,240
I'm not up for it.

147
00:08:51,559 --> 00:08:52,440
Go for it this time.

148
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,679
You have my full support.

149
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:54,559
Give it your all.

150
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:58,759
Everyone, recognize this opportunity.

151
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:17,440
Congrats.

152
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:19,720
Thank you, Barry.

153
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:22,399
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

154
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:23,279
Cheers.

155
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:29,080
You have no idea

156
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:32,039
how much my head was aching
for this position during this time.

157
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:34,159
And now with everything settled,

158
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:36,480
I can finally have a good night's sleep.

159
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:40,080
Going forward, we'll be counting
on you in the Sales Department.

160
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,840
Don't say that. There's also Peter.

161
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:45,080
Actually,
I need to rely on you the most.

162
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:47,039
Next year's targets
will be really daunting.

163
00:09:47,039 --> 00:09:49,559
Could you two
put the work aside for a bit?

164
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:52,559
The big boss has spoken. Okay.

165
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:55,279
So can we tell Dong Yue the secrets now?

166
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:55,799
Yes.

167
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,159
What secrets?

168
00:09:57,799 --> 00:10:01,279
Secrets you wouldn't know
before becoming Sales Director.

169
00:10:02,159 --> 00:10:02,960
You tell him.

170
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:03,600
Okay.

171
00:10:04,799 --> 00:10:08,159
As you know,
since GST first entered China,

172
00:10:08,279 --> 00:10:12,320
it's been about co-building success
and growing together with distributors.

173
00:10:12,559 --> 00:10:16,600
So every Sales Director
isn't just appointed by the company,

174
00:10:16,679 --> 00:10:18,919
but must also earn recognition
from distributors.

175
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:23,440
That's why the first thing
every new Sales Director does

176
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:25,600
is paying respects to the distributors.

177
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,639
Shen Mo?

178
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,080
He'll give you some tests.

179
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:34,840
Like making you strip
and jump into the ocean.

180
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:36,919
Xu Yuntian served two terms
as Sales Director.

181
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:38,159
I remember the second time,

182
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:43,600
Shen Mo made him perform the lion dance
in women's high heels, right?

183
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,080
I remember that.

184
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:49,519
He was so mad that
he threw things around that time.

185
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:52,320
But Shen Mo probably
won't give you such a hard time.

186
00:10:52,559 --> 00:10:53,200
He won't.

187
00:10:53,759 --> 00:10:55,320
You're going to marry his daughter.

188
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:59,440
Gentlemen, go to eat.

189
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:22,759
Mr. Li, it's been too long
since we met privately.

190
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,000
We could go to my place.

191
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:32,159
It's nearby, just a few minutes' walk.

192
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:34,320
Why did you go see Zhao Mei?

193
00:11:35,279 --> 00:11:36,080
I didn't.

194
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:38,399
I was at a meeting near Liyun Hotel.

195
00:11:38,919 --> 00:11:39,919
I went to do my hair

196
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,200
and ran into her.

197
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:43,519
So you went to a meeting,
did your hair, and ran into her?

198
00:11:43,519 --> 00:11:45,320
And you got the exact same hairstyle?

199
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,559
Yeah, I felt a connection with her.

200
00:11:48,559 --> 00:11:50,559
Qiao Hailun, I know what's on your mind.

201
00:11:50,679 --> 00:11:52,519
I made myself very clear
to you last time.

202
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:54,159
Don't cross my line.

203
00:11:54,799 --> 00:11:56,039
If you dare see her again,

204
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:57,440
I won't be nice to you.

205
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,039
Mr. Li.

206
00:12:08,279 --> 00:12:08,840
Mr. Li.

207
00:12:09,279 --> 00:12:10,519
Mr. Li, listen to me.

208
00:12:11,039 --> 00:12:14,840
Mr. Li. Wait, Mr. Li.

209
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,360
Mr. Li, listen to me.

210
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,840
You've got it all wrong. You really do.

211
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:21,039
It's really not what you think.
I know you have a family.

212
00:12:21,039 --> 00:12:22,679
I would never do anything inappropriate.

213
00:12:22,679 --> 00:12:26,399
I... I just want
to come back to your team

214
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:27,440
to keep working for you.

215
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,919
I just ran into her by chance today.

216
00:12:30,559 --> 00:12:32,159
Really, it was purely coincidental.

217
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:33,960
So many coincidences in this world, huh?

218
00:12:34,919 --> 00:12:37,840
Maybe the company could coincidentally
discover your kickbacks one day.

219
00:12:38,399 --> 00:12:39,399
What kickbacks?

220
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,759
I haven't taken any kickbacks.

221
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:44,159
You took a 120,000 kickback
on the Wan Jialing project.

222
00:12:44,159 --> 00:12:45,000
You've forgotten?

223
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:49,960
Mr. Yu from Wan Jialing gave me a card

224
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:53,440
as extra appreciation for my help.

225
00:12:55,159 --> 00:12:56,008
How much is in there?

226
00:12:58,679 --> 00:12:59,480
Quite a lot.

227
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:01,240
120,000 yuan.

228
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:05,200
But I didn't take it.
They gave it to me.

229
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,559
I even specifically asked you.
You told me to accept it.

230
00:13:07,559 --> 00:13:09,440
120,000 yuan isn't a small amount.

231
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,679
Enough to land you in jail.

232
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,679
You set this up, didn't you?

233
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,919
You set this up. It was all your doing.

234
00:13:16,919 --> 00:13:17,960
Why did you do this to me?

235
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,240
What exactly did I do wrong?

236
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,840
We didn't have to end up like this.

237
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,360
You pushed me to this.

238
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,480
Don't go see her again.

239
00:13:25,279 --> 00:13:26,080
Remember that.

240
00:13:37,919 --> 00:13:39,039
What did I do wrong?

241
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,559
What did I do wrong?

242
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:44,960
What did I do wrong?

243
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:48,320
Ms. Qiao,

244
00:13:48,519 --> 00:13:49,919
your bag and phone.

245
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,919
Guan, give them to me.
I'll take them to Ms. Qiao.

246
00:13:53,919 --> 00:13:54,919
Okay, here you are.

247
00:13:54,919 --> 00:13:55,919
Give them to her for me.

248
00:13:55,919 --> 00:13:56,759
Alright, okay.

249
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:02,799
Ms. Qiao.

250
00:14:04,679 --> 00:14:05,200
Ms. Qiao.

251
00:14:07,559 --> 00:14:08,519
Your bag and phone.

252
00:14:14,159 --> 00:14:14,759
Thank you.

253
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,159
I remember.

254
00:14:20,559 --> 00:14:21,799
I remember.

255
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,559
I remember.

256
00:14:27,679 --> 00:14:28,440
Ms. Qiao,

257
00:14:28,919 --> 00:14:30,480
if anyone bullies you, don't be afraid.

258
00:14:30,799 --> 00:14:31,679
You're my friend.

259
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:32,960
I... I lack great skills.

260
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:33,840
But I'm strong.

261
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:34,360
Maybe...

262
00:14:34,919 --> 00:14:37,039
Maybe I can go and beat him up for you.
How's that?

263
00:14:43,279 --> 00:14:44,679
Really, Ms. Qiao, I'll beat him up.

264
00:14:48,879 --> 00:14:49,759
What did you say?

265
00:14:52,639 --> 00:14:54,039
He's my boyfriend.

266
00:14:55,519 --> 00:14:57,360
He's my boyfriend.

267
00:14:58,320 --> 00:15:00,519
He's my boyfriend.

268
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:03,120
He has no right to treat you like that.

269
00:15:03,679 --> 00:15:04,440
No.

270
00:15:05,279 --> 00:15:06,559
He's my boss.

271
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:09,840
He's my boss.

272
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:15,399
I'm the most despicable woman
in the world.

273
00:15:16,559 --> 00:15:20,440
I'm the most despicable woman
in the world.

274
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:27,279
Just leave me alone from now on.

275
00:15:27,919 --> 00:15:30,440
I'm the most despicable person
in the world.

276
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,440
I knew you'd come.

277
00:15:57,919 --> 00:15:59,320
Don't bother. No slippers for you.

278
00:16:02,159 --> 00:16:03,440
Zhao Mei, are you hungry?

279
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:06,399
How about we grab some supper later?

280
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:07,960
No need.

281
00:16:10,039 --> 00:16:12,200
This must be the dog
you posted about on Moments.

282
00:16:12,679 --> 00:16:13,360
So cute.

283
00:16:29,799 --> 00:16:30,279
What?

284
00:16:30,919 --> 00:16:32,000
Equity Transfer Agreement.

285
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:34,799
Sign it.

286
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:37,480
Then the three percent of Momili shares
will be yours.

287
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:41,480
I want to use this
to earn your forgiveness.

288
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,000
I've made up my mind.

289
00:16:45,919 --> 00:16:46,799
I want a divorce.

290
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:49,039
Why must you do this?

291
00:16:49,559 --> 00:16:51,279
What good will divorcing me do you?

292
00:16:51,679 --> 00:16:53,279
If Barry finds out we're divorcing...

293
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:54,759
Can you stop mentioning these to me?

294
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,279
Things like "what good".

295
00:16:58,279 --> 00:16:59,799
Marrying you was good for me.

296
00:16:59,799 --> 00:17:01,840
Not announcing it publicly
was also good for me.

297
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:05,400
You always use "it's good for me"
as a reason to make me obey you.

298
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:07,039
Li Dongming,

299
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:09,400
I actually really
dislike this tone of yours.

300
00:17:09,799 --> 00:17:11,960
It has nothing to do with who benefits.

301
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:13,839
I'm divorcing you
because you had an affair.

302
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:15,759
I can't accept it, and that's all.

303
00:17:19,559 --> 00:17:21,400
I didn't expect you
to still be so naive.

304
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,079
You're a grown woman.

305
00:17:23,079 --> 00:17:24,680
Don't you know yourself well enough?

306
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,680
You're naturally drawn
to the powerful one.

307
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:28,799
What do you mean?

308
00:17:28,799 --> 00:17:30,319
If you admit that,

309
00:17:30,319 --> 00:17:32,119
you shouldn't dwell
on this mistake of mine.

310
00:17:32,319 --> 00:17:34,200
I did you wrong.

311
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:35,680
I understand your anger.

312
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:38,519
But try to see it from my perspective.

313
00:17:38,519 --> 00:17:41,079
I've climbed step by step
to where I am today.

314
00:17:41,279 --> 00:17:42,248
I've had some success.

315
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,440
What drives me?

316
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:45,319
What rewards does society give me?

317
00:17:45,839 --> 00:17:48,839
Nothing but money, status, and women.

318
00:17:49,319 --> 00:17:50,559
You might not like this,

319
00:17:50,559 --> 00:17:53,039
but it's in men's nature
to want to possess more women.

320
00:17:53,039 --> 00:17:54,440
It's hardwired into male DNA.

321
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,839
I love you deeply.

322
00:17:55,839 --> 00:17:57,240
That's beyond doubt.

323
00:17:57,519 --> 00:17:59,400
But sometimes,

324
00:17:59,839 --> 00:18:03,079
my body and my mind
crave some extra rewards.

325
00:18:03,079 --> 00:18:07,680
This is what men like Xu Yuntian and me,
men with real masculine drive, all want.

326
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:08,799
What do you mean by that?

327
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:10,200
That's one-sided.

328
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:11,000
Name one.

329
00:18:11,519 --> 00:18:12,640
My dad and your dad.

330
00:18:12,839 --> 00:18:14,440
That's because they lacked the means.

331
00:18:14,839 --> 00:18:15,480
(Laughable.)

332
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:18,200
(He thinks he speaks for all men)

333
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,240
(and twists logic.)

334
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:20,920
(That's Li Dongming,)

335
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:22,720
(turning black into white.)

336
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,319
(He won't change.)

337
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:27,440
It'll just be a vicious cycle.

338
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:32,240
You know what?
While you were lecturing me just now,

339
00:18:32,359 --> 00:18:35,079
it only strengthened my resolve
to divorce you.

340
00:18:35,079 --> 00:18:37,079
Those women might be rewards to you,

341
00:18:37,079 --> 00:18:39,240
but to me, they're a huge punishment.

342
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:41,880
I can't accept punishment for no fault
and swallow my pride.

343
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:43,240
Times have changed, Li Dongming.

344
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:46,480
No matter how things change,
male and female genes won't.

345
00:18:47,079 --> 00:18:48,119
Human nature won't change.

346
00:18:50,799 --> 00:18:52,559
I don't know if men will change,

347
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:56,519
but women will.
We'll learn to love ourselves more.

348
00:18:57,279 --> 00:18:59,400
You're right. I admire the powerful one.

349
00:19:01,599 --> 00:19:03,880
But now, I only want
to admire my own power.

350
00:19:04,799 --> 00:19:06,839
When I'm strong,
that's what really matters.

351
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:17,359
We're closing up.

352
00:19:22,759 --> 00:19:24,240
You're here again?

353
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,880
So much trouble, huh?

354
00:19:27,279 --> 00:19:27,960
I got promoted.

355
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:31,000
That's great.

356
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:31,799
Congrats!

357
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,920
Let me make you a coffee.

358
00:19:34,279 --> 00:19:35,240
It's free.

359
00:19:37,039 --> 00:19:37,480
Thanks.

360
00:19:51,176 --> 00:19:51,861
(Hello!)

361
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:53,448
(My dad said you got promoted.)

362
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:54,400
(Congrats.)

363
00:19:54,599 --> 00:19:56,559
(He finally found you as his successor.)

364
00:19:57,319 --> 00:19:59,000
(Actually, it's good to have you.)

365
00:19:59,319 --> 00:20:01,319
(I really couldn't
handle things in his company.)

366
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:04,839
(By the way, he said you'll pay respects
at the club tomorrow, right?)

367
00:20:06,039 --> 00:20:07,039
(I'll go too tomorrow.)

368
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,960
(If anyone bothers you,
I'll make them pay.)

369
00:20:13,128 --> 00:20:18,137
(Yongzheng Hall)

370
00:20:36,039 --> 00:20:37,359
You're here. Just a second.

371
00:20:37,359 --> 00:20:38,079
Almost done here.

372
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:39,359
- Mr. Shen.
- Dong Yue.

373
00:20:40,039 --> 00:20:41,799
Here you are. Congrats.

374
00:20:42,839 --> 00:20:44,839
I was just discussing
the ceremony later.

375
00:20:46,079 --> 00:20:47,000
Don't be nervous.

376
00:20:47,559 --> 00:20:49,680
I won't ask you to move mountains.

377
00:20:50,759 --> 00:20:51,440
Thank you.

378
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:54,319
I heard you've not been well recently.

379
00:20:55,279 --> 00:20:58,200
Yes, some heart trouble.

380
00:20:58,839 --> 00:20:59,640
It has a hole.

381
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:02,000
So I asked the doctor,

382
00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:03,960
"If I drink in the future,

383
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:06,279
will the liquor go in one end

384
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:08,279
and flow out the other?"

385
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:13,279
The doctor told me to see a psychiatrist
before surgery.

386
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,079
You'll have a surgery?

387
00:21:15,119 --> 00:21:15,640
When?

388
00:21:16,279 --> 00:21:17,279
I haven't set a date yet.

389
00:21:17,799 --> 00:21:18,559
When I have time.

390
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:20,599
Enough about that.

391
00:21:20,599 --> 00:21:21,720
Today's your big day.

392
00:21:22,359 --> 00:21:22,920
By the way,

393
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:26,160
I heard a subordinate
actually took the fall

394
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:29,279
for Zhao Mei in her bribery case.

395
00:21:30,599 --> 00:21:31,400
I didn't expect

396
00:21:31,559 --> 00:21:34,039
a woman to inspire such loyalty.

397
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:38,440
Mr. Shen, everything's ready.

398
00:21:38,839 --> 00:21:39,160
Okay.

399
00:21:40,559 --> 00:21:41,400
You're Lu Ting?

400
00:21:42,319 --> 00:21:44,200
I am. How can I help you?

401
00:21:44,559 --> 00:21:47,319
You gave that dog to Zhao Mei?

402
00:21:47,599 --> 00:21:49,319
I told her to do that. Any problem?

403
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:51,079
No.

404
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:53,359
Alright. Come on, let's go in.

405
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:54,880
This way.

406
00:21:57,839 --> 00:21:58,400
Shen Xing.

407
00:21:58,839 --> 00:21:59,680
Coming.

408
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:01,599
Everyone, we can get seated now.

409
00:22:02,880 --> 00:22:03,359
Mr. Shen.

410
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:05,519
Congrats.

411
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:07,640
Mr. Dong, congratulations.

412
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:10,559
This is Zhuang Zhiqiang
from An Province.

413
00:22:11,039 --> 00:22:11,559
A big boss.

414
00:22:12,319 --> 00:22:12,960
You flatter me.

415
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:14,720
I'm hardly a boss compared to you.

416
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:18,079
This is Mr. Lin from Houjue Industries.

417
00:22:19,359 --> 00:22:21,880
Right, you two know each other.

418
00:22:22,079 --> 00:22:23,440
This is Mr. Zhuang.

419
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:25,319
He came all the way from An Province.

420
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:26,680
Hello.

421
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:28,240
Mr. Lin from Houjue Industries.

422
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:29,519
We call him Lin.

423
00:22:29,519 --> 00:22:30,440
Forthright man.

424
00:22:30,799 --> 00:22:31,640
Hello, Mr. Lin.

425
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:33,119
Familiar, right?

426
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:35,079
I didn't expect to see you here.

427
00:22:35,839 --> 00:22:37,000
Congrats on your promotion.

428
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:37,672
It's all fate.

429
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:40,960
We have to thank Mr. Shen
for giving us this opportunity.

430
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:43,240
So we can learn from you.

431
00:22:43,359 --> 00:22:43,799
Right.

432
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:44,799
You flatter me.

433
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:45,799
Congrats, Mr. Shen.

434
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:47,759
Having a capable son-in-law
like Mr. Dong

435
00:22:47,759 --> 00:22:49,000
will give you a huge edge.

436
00:22:49,319 --> 00:22:53,240
Everyone, the imported liquor field
will be Mr. Shen's domain from now on.

437
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:54,880
We just need to follow him.

438
00:22:55,160 --> 00:22:55,640
Right.

439
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:56,599
Alright.

440
00:22:56,599 --> 00:22:58,880
I'm not the star today. He is.

441
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:00,200
Let's begin.

442
00:23:00,319 --> 00:23:01,119
- Okay.
- Okay.

443
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:02,519
Mr. Shen, please sit.

444
00:23:06,079 --> 00:23:08,000
Today, as per Mr. Shen's instructions,

445
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:13,480
the pre-dinner ritual we've prepared
for Mr. Dong is the lo hei ceremony,

446
00:23:13,759 --> 00:23:15,119
also known as the prosperity toss.

447
00:23:15,559 --> 00:23:17,440
It symbolizes a thriving
and prosperous future.

448
00:23:18,599 --> 00:23:19,519
- Great.
- Great.

449
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:23,368
Mr. Shen.

450
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:25,672
Give them to him.

451
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:27,759
Look at me.

452
00:23:29,559 --> 00:23:30,079
Mr. Dong.

453
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:33,000
You sit too.

454
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:42,680
After today,
you'll be GST's Sales Director.

455
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:47,680
When you get back, fire Zhao Mei.

456
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:50,400
It's not a personal bias.

457
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:54,640
But the Promotions Department head
should be one of our own.

458
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:56,240
I've picked someone for you.

459
00:23:57,720 --> 00:23:59,319
Lu Ting. How about her?

460
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:03,039
Is there no man
in your Promotions Department?

461
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:05,759
Despite her youth,

462
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:07,240
she's very smart,

463
00:24:07,519 --> 00:24:08,119
methodical,

464
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:08,960
responsible,

465
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:10,200
and bold yet meticulous.

466
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:11,839
She's excellent.

467
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:13,960
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

468
00:24:14,079 --> 00:24:15,400
From now on, stick with Dong Yue.

469
00:24:15,839 --> 00:24:18,559
Following him, your future is promising.

470
00:24:19,680 --> 00:24:21,839
If I have the chance
to learn from Mr. Dong,

471
00:24:21,839 --> 00:24:23,519
of course, I'd feel honored.

472
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,079
I won't need you.

473
00:24:40,839 --> 00:24:44,119
I'm afraid one day
you might send me a dog too.

474
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:47,079
A dog? What dog?

475
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:48,480
What?

476
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:51,960
What dog?

477
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:55,799
Just a dog.

478
00:25:07,039 --> 00:25:08,680
I think Dong Yue and I

479
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:12,279
still need to talk.

480
00:25:13,519 --> 00:25:15,960
I have something to take care of.
I'll make a call outside.

481
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:16,519
Right.

482
00:25:16,519 --> 00:25:17,640
Everyone, this way please.

483
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:18,039
Right.

484
00:25:18,039 --> 00:25:18,600
This way.

485
00:25:20,279 --> 00:25:21,400
- After you.
- I'll go to your place.

486
00:25:25,599 --> 00:25:26,279
It's over?

487
00:25:27,119 --> 00:25:28,240
I'll wait for you outside.

488
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:39,960
What?

489
00:25:42,039 --> 00:25:43,839
You can't bear to fire Zhao Mei?

490
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:46,039
That's too ruthless.

491
00:25:47,799 --> 00:25:48,559
Don't you think so?

492
00:25:49,880 --> 00:25:50,599
Ruthless?

493
00:25:52,440 --> 00:25:53,200
I don't think so.

494
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:56,319
I just want her out of the way.

495
00:25:58,400 --> 00:25:59,319
I told you

496
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:01,559
I don't like Zhao Mei.

497
00:26:03,119 --> 00:26:03,759
Why?

498
00:26:04,759 --> 00:26:06,376
A woman's heart is the most poisonous.

499
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:08,359
Look at her.

500
00:26:09,359 --> 00:26:09,960
She can endure.

501
00:26:11,319 --> 00:26:14,000
She had endured
for ten years under Xu Yuntian.

502
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:15,368
She's ruthless.

503
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:18,279
She could take down Tang Lide
immediately

504
00:26:19,279 --> 00:26:21,279
and turn against Xu Yuntian
without hesitation.

505
00:26:21,839 --> 00:26:24,920
If a woman like that
becomes Sales Director,

506
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:30,799
she will replace you, me, and all
the other veteran distributors

507
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,232
with her own people right away.

508
00:26:33,079 --> 00:26:35,160
So I can't let her climb any higher.

509
00:26:36,519 --> 00:26:39,960
Nor can I allow her to work under you.

510
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:42,319
Do you understand?

511
00:26:47,359 --> 00:26:48,359
I know your thoughts.

512
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:53,480
You're afraid I'll use the same methods
against you someday.

513
00:26:54,519 --> 00:26:55,319
How could I?

514
00:26:56,119 --> 00:26:58,079
Putting aside your relationship
with Shen Xing,

515
00:26:58,759 --> 00:27:00,200
I've always had high hopes for you.

516
00:27:00,599 --> 00:27:01,759
I want to help you succeed.

517
00:27:03,799 --> 00:27:04,319
Of course,

518
00:27:09,759 --> 00:27:11,039
I hope you'll appreciate it.

519
00:27:30,759 --> 00:27:31,319
Mr. Shen,

520
00:27:32,559 --> 00:27:33,160
I'm sorry.

521
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:39,200
Thank you for looking out for me
all this time.

522
00:27:58,559 --> 00:28:02,640
But I can't accept your way
of doing things.

523
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:06,599
You can't accept it?

524
00:28:07,680 --> 00:28:09,960
Then how come you accepted it
when you set up Xu Yuntian?

525
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:16,160
Don't forget,

526
00:28:18,119 --> 00:28:21,160
the sexual harassment trap
was your idea.

527
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:25,319
A hug and a kiss

528
00:28:26,359 --> 00:28:28,279
were enough to take down Xu Yuntian.

529
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:29,720
By that standard,

530
00:28:30,880 --> 00:28:33,680
we'd all be lined up and shot.

531
00:28:34,599 --> 00:28:35,839
I just can't get this world.

532
00:28:37,119 --> 00:28:38,960
As the one who could devise such a plan,

533
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:42,240
you are now suddenly
preaching virtues to me?

534
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:44,640
Mr. Shen, to be honest,

535
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:48,960
I regretted what happened to Mr. Xu
that very night.

536
00:28:50,359 --> 00:28:51,160
Why?

537
00:28:51,880 --> 00:28:52,839
I wasn't happy about it.

538
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:58,720
I was terrified
that I might end up like him one day.

539
00:28:59,599 --> 00:29:01,000
Maybe that's how our industry is.

540
00:29:02,240 --> 00:29:03,519
We stumble our way up

541
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:06,279
and stumble our way down.

542
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:09,440
What exactly do you want?

543
00:29:11,599 --> 00:29:12,559
To turn against me?

544
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,960
You're the Sales Director now.

545
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:18,240
You'll inevitably deal with me.

546
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:23,480
Or do you think you have what it takes
to take me down?

547
00:29:28,519 --> 00:29:29,720
You wouldn't understand.

548
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:34,519
Goodbye.

549
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:43,599
Dong Yue?

550
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:44,920
Why are you leaving?

551
00:29:45,319 --> 00:29:46,519
What did he say to you?

552
00:29:47,119 --> 00:29:49,119
I told you long ago he's not nice.

553
00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:51,680
Whatever he said,
don't take it to heart, okay?

554
00:29:51,759 --> 00:29:52,759
I also want to tell you

555
00:29:52,759 --> 00:29:53,960
it's better if we break up.

556
00:29:54,599 --> 00:29:55,440
Why?

557
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:57,640
Didn't we agree before not to break up?

558
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:59,200
What exactly did he say to you?

559
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:00,200
No, it's not his problem.

560
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:01,000
It's my own problem.

561
00:30:02,319 --> 00:30:03,559
I don't love you anymore, okay?

562
00:30:03,559 --> 00:30:04,440
I don't accept that.

563
00:30:04,759 --> 00:30:06,000
You said you loved me.

564
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,880
You said I was cute and special.

565
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:09,599
How can you suddenly stop loving me?

566
00:30:09,599 --> 00:30:11,079
Yes, when we first got together,

567
00:30:11,079 --> 00:30:13,799
I... I genuinely thought
you were very cute.

568
00:30:13,799 --> 00:30:14,640
I liked you a lot.

569
00:30:15,319 --> 00:30:17,200
Not long after we got together,
I got promoted.

570
00:30:17,559 --> 00:30:18,440
I only found out later

571
00:30:18,839 --> 00:30:20,079
that your father is Shen Mo.

572
00:30:20,079 --> 00:30:21,240
That's why I rose so fast.

573
00:30:21,240 --> 00:30:23,240
No one at GST rose that fast.

574
00:30:23,799 --> 00:30:25,480
But what's wrong with that?

575
00:30:25,759 --> 00:30:27,000
Do you hate being promoted?

576
00:30:27,079 --> 00:30:28,880
Our industry runs on connections.

577
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:31,640
Your father being my top distributor
isn't a bad thing for me at all.

578
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:33,480
But I'm confused too.

579
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:34,920
I keep wondering,

580
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:38,640
would I have risen so fast
if I weren't your boyfriend?

581
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,200
The answer is no.

582
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:42,079
Not even if my performance was stellar.

583
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:45,920
And my good performance

584
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:49,400
is largely because my clients
show respect to Mr. Shen.

585
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:51,640
Isn't it good
that I could bring you these things?

586
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:53,880
Do you have a problem with that?

587
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:54,880
I don't have a problem.

588
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:01,000
I don't have a problem.

589
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:08,559
I love someone else.

590
00:31:12,519 --> 00:31:15,880
I'm willing to give up everything
for that relationship.

591
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:18,880
I don't love you.

592
00:31:19,528 --> 00:31:21,200
♪Too much of shame♪

593
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:21,720
I'm sorry.

594
00:31:21,794 --> 00:31:24,590
♪To waste it crying♪

595
00:31:27,048 --> 00:31:28,968
♪Leave all behind you♪

596
00:31:28,968 --> 00:31:31,248
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

597
00:31:31,368 --> 00:31:33,597
♪You know how far you've gone♪

598
00:31:33,732 --> 00:31:35,720
♪In the fire you rise again♪

599
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:36,640
(I'm happy.)

600
00:31:37,720 --> 00:31:38,599
(In all this time,)

601
00:31:38,599 --> 00:31:41,279
(for the first time,
I told Shen Mo how I truly felt.)

602
00:31:42,559 --> 00:31:44,119
(Just thinking about his stunned look)

603
00:31:44,599 --> 00:31:45,680
(makes me smile.)

604
00:31:47,240 --> 00:31:49,160
(He must be unaccustomed
to being rejected.)

605
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:52,599
(I paid the price of resigning.)

606
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:54,000
(But I have to say)

607
00:31:54,664 --> 00:31:57,680
(Resignation)
(it feels great to tell the truth.)

608
00:31:58,161 --> 00:32:00,377
♪Countless expenses burning up♪

609
00:32:00,377 --> 00:32:01,729
♪But you know♪

610
00:32:01,729 --> 00:32:02,962
♪Pressure upon opening my eyes♪

611
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:07,880
Fang,

612
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:09,880
are you really going back?

613
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:13,000
Right, Fang, Chinese New Year is coming.

614
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:15,000
If you leave now,
you won't even get your bonus.

615
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:16,720
Why would I need that bonus?

616
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,359
It's just one or two thousand yuan.

617
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:20,839
It could barely

618
00:32:21,279 --> 00:32:22,680
cover my food and rent.

619
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:26,160
I started as a promoter ten years ago.

620
00:32:26,519 --> 00:32:28,359
Ten years later, I'm still a promoter.

621
00:32:28,759 --> 00:32:31,240
If I stay any longer,
I might be a promoter for life.

622
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:32,960
I've had enough.

623
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:35,000
I wake up in a cold sweat.

624
00:32:40,839 --> 00:32:43,000
I have no idea
what I've done these past ten years.

625
00:32:43,240 --> 00:32:44,759
What am I after? You tell me.

626
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:45,920
I have no money

627
00:32:46,039 --> 00:32:47,319
and no man either.

628
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:48,640
When I go back home,

629
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:51,000
people think I've struck it rich
in Guangzhou.

630
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:53,000
Do I look like a rich person?

631
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,039
Seriously.

632
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:56,200
Right?

633
00:33:00,599 --> 00:33:01,599
What are you all doing?

634
00:33:02,759 --> 00:33:04,008
It's a farewell, not a funeral.

635
00:33:05,319 --> 00:33:06,240
Don't pull this act.

636
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:08,480
I'm leaving.

637
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:09,640
It's what you like.

638
00:33:09,640 --> 00:33:10,279
No.

639
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:13,119
No one sees me off. I'll go alone.

640
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:18,680
Can I have one more hug, Fang?

641
00:33:22,480 --> 00:33:23,079
Okay.

642
00:33:24,799 --> 00:33:25,256
Let's hug.

643
00:33:32,440 --> 00:33:33,400
Take care.

644
00:33:37,119 --> 00:33:38,759
You better not bully her.

645
00:33:46,119 --> 00:33:47,000
Zeng Zixuan.

646
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:50,240
You're the most promising one among us.

647
00:33:52,759 --> 00:33:53,160
Come on.

648
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:00,559
Take care.

649
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:09,920
Don't do this. Come on.

650
00:34:15,119 --> 00:34:15,920
See you around.

651
00:34:53,119 --> 00:34:53,719
Tong.

652
00:34:57,800 --> 00:34:59,559
Have everyone get together tonight.

653
00:34:59,920 --> 00:35:01,559
It's like a farewell dinner
for Wang Hao.

654
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:04,559
Don't use department funds.

655
00:35:04,679 --> 00:35:06,400
The standard is low.
I'll cover the cost.

656
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:07,719
Okay.

657
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,320
Go book a nice place.

658
00:35:09,840 --> 00:35:12,079
We wanted to go to that Ten Years place.

659
00:35:12,079 --> 00:35:13,559
But now it's way too hyped.

660
00:35:13,559 --> 00:35:14,400
It is always packed.

661
00:35:14,400 --> 00:35:15,400
It's impossible to book.

662
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:17,360
Okay, I know the owner of Ten Years.

663
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,320
I'll contact him.

664
00:35:18,760 --> 00:35:19,599
You go ask everyone.

665
00:35:19,599 --> 00:35:20,039
Okay.

666
00:35:21,096 --> 00:35:23,656
(Hetai Center)

667
00:35:26,239 --> 00:35:27,239
What are you doing now?

668
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,519
I'm eating.

669
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:30,840
Can you talk on the phone?

670
00:35:32,039 --> 00:35:34,440
Tonight, let's drink first

671
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:35,880
and not worry about tomorrow.

672
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:38,119
I'm at the hospital now.

673
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:40,280
I just completed the admission
for Shen Mo.

674
00:35:40,559 --> 00:35:42,248
He's having a surgery
in a couple of days.

675
00:35:43,159 --> 00:35:43,960
Here's the thing.

676
00:35:43,960 --> 00:35:45,840
I was chatting with him
and mentioned you.

677
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:48,800
It seems he's fallen out with Dong Yue.

678
00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:50,079
Then he asked me

679
00:35:50,199 --> 00:35:51,559
if you're involved with Dong Yue.

680
00:35:51,559 --> 00:35:53,032
I said no, but he didn't believe me.

681
00:35:53,559 --> 00:35:55,960
Then he mentioned
the secretly taken photo of you two.

682
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:58,719
It just occurred to me.

683
00:35:58,800 --> 00:36:01,079
I think I saw the person
who took that photo of you.

684
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:04,480
That day, I was afraid Shen Mo
would keep giving you a hard time.

685
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:07,039
So I just invited him outside.

686
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:10,039
We had chatted and walked outside
for a long time.

687
00:36:11,599 --> 00:36:13,440
After that,
I walked him back to his room.

688
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:14,960
You remember?

689
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:16,679
You and I stayed on the same floor.

690
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:18,599
When I left the elevator,

691
00:36:18,599 --> 00:36:19,840
I saw Zeng Zixuan.

692
00:36:20,079 --> 00:36:21,679
She was standing there
holding her phone.

693
00:36:23,039 --> 00:36:25,519
And she didn't greet me back,
and her expression was strange.

694
00:36:26,239 --> 00:36:27,360
Now that I think back,

695
00:36:27,559 --> 00:36:28,760
combined with the time,

696
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:29,960
location,

697
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:31,119
and angle,

698
00:36:31,599 --> 00:36:34,079
I'm sure she's the one
who took the photo secretly.

699
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:35,719
Zeng Zixuan?

700
00:36:37,079 --> 00:36:38,079
It was her?

701
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:40,039
Binbin, you two
aren't in the same group.

702
00:36:41,039 --> 00:36:41,519
You two...

703
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,760
You are.

704
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:44,599
Binbin, you're with Tong.

705
00:36:44,599 --> 00:36:45,280
Right.

706
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:45,679
Right.

707
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,360
I was the one who hired you.

708
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:49,360
Guess I'm the exception.

709
00:36:49,360 --> 00:36:50,360
You're the exception.

710
00:36:52,320 --> 00:36:53,079
How's the drinking?

711
00:36:53,079 --> 00:36:53,719
Pretty well.

712
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:56,079
I'm sorry.

713
00:36:56,159 --> 00:36:57,280
Hao, I'm late.

714
00:36:58,400 --> 00:36:59,559
Something came up just now.

715
00:37:02,880 --> 00:37:04,599
But why would she take that photo of us?

716
00:37:04,599 --> 00:37:05,360
How should I know?

717
00:37:06,440 --> 00:37:08,079
Young girls today have strange ideas.

718
00:37:08,079 --> 00:37:09,119
Different from our time.

719
00:37:10,079 --> 00:37:11,519
Everyone's here. I'd like a toast.

720
00:37:12,840 --> 00:37:14,159
Thank you all

721
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:17,199
for organizing
this farewell dinner for me.

722
00:37:18,039 --> 00:37:20,239
As you know,
I'm not particularly good with words.

723
00:37:20,719 --> 00:37:21,480
I...

724
00:37:23,199 --> 00:37:24,320
Thank you all. Bottoms up!

725
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:24,960
Alright.

726
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:26,280
- Enough, Hao.
- I'll finish mine.

727
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:26,792
Bottoms up!

728
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:37,480
Hao.

729
00:37:40,199 --> 00:37:41,840
Mei.

730
00:37:44,559 --> 00:37:47,239
It's been over four years
since I joined GST.

731
00:37:48,159 --> 00:37:49,199
I still remember

732
00:37:49,199 --> 00:37:53,159
the scene from my first day
interviewing at the company.

733
00:37:53,639 --> 00:37:55,840
From that day on,
I was determined to work for you.

734
00:37:57,199 --> 00:37:59,760
I even thought that if I never found
my own purpose in life,

735
00:37:59,760 --> 00:38:01,239
I'd make following you my goal.

736
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,239
It's... it's just that...

737
00:38:10,280 --> 00:38:10,719
Alright.

738
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:13,280
Having worked together

739
00:38:14,199 --> 00:38:15,159
is a privilege to me.

740
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:18,120
Come on.

741
00:38:23,559 --> 00:38:26,920
Mei, having worked with you
is a privilege to me too.

742
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:27,840
Don't drink anymore.

743
00:38:28,519 --> 00:38:29,679
I-I-I'll toast to you.

744
00:38:30,159 --> 00:38:31,400
No, let's all drink together.

745
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:32,079
Together.

746
00:38:32,079 --> 00:38:32,480
Cheers!

747
00:38:33,519 --> 00:38:34,679
Let's all do it together.

748
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:35,840
I'll check on the dishes.

749
00:38:37,920 --> 00:38:38,599
Together.

750
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:42,400
(I always knew this girl wasn't simple.)

751
00:38:43,039 --> 00:38:45,519
(But her taking the photo
of Dong Yue and me to report us)

752
00:38:46,199 --> 00:38:47,880
(still exceeded my expectations.)

753
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:50,079
Hold on.

754
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:52,199
(Don't all young people
want to slack off?)

755
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:54,800
(Since when did they become so caring?)

756
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:58,719
(Could Liang Danning
be overthinking it?)

757
00:39:00,440 --> 00:39:02,639
(No, I need to verify this.)

758
00:39:51,483 --> 00:39:56,223
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

759
00:40:00,673 --> 00:40:02,593
♪Too much of shame♪

760
00:40:02,939 --> 00:40:05,735
♪To waste it crying♪

761
00:40:08,193 --> 00:40:10,113
♪Leave all behind you♪

762
00:40:10,113 --> 00:40:12,393
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

763
00:40:12,513 --> 00:40:14,742
♪You know how far you've gone♪

764
00:40:14,877 --> 00:40:17,153
♪In the fire you rise again♪

765
00:40:17,339 --> 00:40:19,699
♪You made it through the worst♪

766
00:40:19,837 --> 00:40:22,041
♪The best is yet to come♪

767
00:40:22,284 --> 00:40:24,424
♪The best is yet to come♪

768
00:40:27,126 --> 00:40:28,449
♪Isn't it magical♪

769
00:40:28,449 --> 00:40:30,081
♪Listen, look,
how beautiful the night is♪

770
00:40:30,113 --> 00:40:32,580
♪With countless lights on,
is someone heartbroken again♪

771
00:40:32,580 --> 00:40:35,033
♪The sound of a heart
shattering on the ground is so crisp♪

772
00:40:35,114 --> 00:40:37,762
♪Turn on a light.
A lonely heart needs comfort♪

773
00:40:37,851 --> 00:40:40,382
♪Sweat, toil, dawn, dusk♪

774
00:40:40,462 --> 00:40:42,684
♪Devaluing self-respect
just for some hot food♪

775
00:40:42,826 --> 00:40:43,907
♪But I don't want to♪

776
00:40:44,016 --> 00:40:46,282
♪Sell dignity at a price,
trampling on past vows♪

777
00:40:46,398 --> 00:40:47,463
♪Until 3 AM♪

778
00:40:47,634 --> 00:40:48,839
♪Locking dreams away in a drawer♪

779
00:40:48,993 --> 00:40:50,226
♪Just to earn some meager profit♪

780
00:40:50,317 --> 00:40:52,681
♪No matter how hard I try,
it only brings sobs♪

781
00:40:52,828 --> 00:40:57,238
♪Renewing yearly, gone with no return,
teetering, utterly bland♪

782
00:41:11,963 --> 00:41:13,399
♪Leave all behind you♪

783
00:41:13,503 --> 00:41:15,990
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

784
00:41:16,173 --> 00:41:18,302
♪You know how far you've gone♪

785
00:41:18,489 --> 00:41:20,829
♪In the fire you rise again♪

786
00:41:20,897 --> 00:41:23,163
♪You made it through the worst♪

787
00:41:23,523 --> 00:41:25,601
♪The best is yet to come♪

788
00:41:25,850 --> 00:41:28,020
♪The best is yet to come♪

789
00:41:30,721 --> 00:41:31,873
♪Isn't it magical♪

790
00:41:31,873 --> 00:41:35,519
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

791
00:41:35,553 --> 00:41:37,409
♪And I see them sparkling♪

792
00:41:37,633 --> 00:41:39,764
♪Nobody knows♪

793
00:41:40,385 --> 00:41:42,295
♪What tomorrow brings♪

794
00:41:42,561 --> 00:41:44,884
♪You made it through the worst♪

795
00:41:45,071 --> 00:41:47,279
♪The best is yet to come♪

796
00:41:47,566 --> 00:41:49,715
♪The best is yet to come♪

797
00:41:50,011 --> 00:41:51,425
♪Isn't it magical♪

798
00:41:51,425 --> 00:41:53,637
♪Feeling uneasy,
yet no one's chasing me♪

799
00:41:53,711 --> 00:41:56,065
♪Retreating step by step,
everything turning to ash♪

800
00:41:56,065 --> 00:41:57,153
♪I'm silent, I'm roaring♪

801
00:41:57,153 --> 00:42:00,604
♪This helplessness
keeps pushing me towards the cliff♪

802
00:42:01,057 --> 00:42:03,331
♪Trembling legs
carry away a shattered soul♪

803
00:42:03,745 --> 00:42:04,609
♪Who wants to be just a passerby♪

804
00:42:04,609 --> 00:42:06,129
♪Isn't it magical♪
